high_descs: Go straight then to the right to face the end of the tv stand.
Pick the keys up from off of the tv stand.
Turn around and go straight to face the lamp in the corner.
Turn the lamp on in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn the lamp on while holding the keys.

high_descs: Go forward and then turn right and to the right again to face the side of the television stand.
Pick the keys up from in front of the television.
Turn around and face the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Pick up keys and turn the lamp on.

high_descs: Walk forward to the left side of the television on your right.
Pick up the key chain that is under the television, on the table.
Turn around and walk forward to the tall lamp in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Examine a key chain by the light of a floor lamp.
